These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, car
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, october
1. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Transport      | car     | airplane      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Sport         | water-polo   | rugby |
| Birthday   | november  | october      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, french
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skiing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, documentary
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the french is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
3. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person watching romance movies##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who's sport is skiing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Nationality    | nigerian        | french    |
| Sport       | ice-hockey         | skiing |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary | romance   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

