.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, tram
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
House: futuristic, ranch-style
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, handball
1. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
2. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Transport   | trike       | tram |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| House   | futuristic | ranch-style |
| Sport           | biathlon        | handball   |

