1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
2. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| City          | edinburgh     | london |
| Hobby         | camping  | dancing   |
| Game   | whist | scrabble       |
| Color           | amber | green    |

