.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, may
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse
House: palace, cottage
City: paris, liverpool
1. the palace house is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
2. the nurse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Birthday          | may         | june    |
| Job           | entrepreneur | nurse   |
| House   | palace   | cottage    |
| City     | paris         | liverpool |

 